---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const rawApiBase = (import.meta.env.PUBLIC_NODE_API_BASE ?? '').trim();
const apiBase = rawApiBase.replace(/\/+$/, '');
---

<Layout
  title="AI 만세력 사주팔자 정밀분석 | Korean Saju Palja Premium Report | ManyTool"
  description="AI 기반 성향 분석, 통계 기반 라이프 인사이트, 데이터 기반 자기이해 리포트를 제공하는 Korean Saju Palja 프리미엄 분석 페이지입니다. 오늘, 이번주, 이번달, 상반기, 하반기, 올해와 중년·말년 흐름까지 정리합니다."
  keywords="AI 만세력, Korean Saju Palja, 사주팔자 정밀분석, AI 기반 성향 분석, 통계 기반 라이프 인사이트, 데이터 기반 자기 이해 리포트, 오늘 운세, 이번주 운세, 이번달 운세"
  canonical="https://manytool.net/ai-manseryeok"
>
  <main class="ledger-shell min-h-screen bg-[#131313] text-[#e5e2e1]">
    <style>
      :global(body) {
        background: #131313;
        color: #e5e2e1;
      }
      .ledger-shell {
        font-family: 'Manrope', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 12% 18%, rgba(233, 195, 73, 0.12), transparent 24%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 78% 22%, rgba(89, 222, 155, 0.08), transparent 22%),
          #131313;
      }
      .ledger-serif { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', 'Noto Serif', serif; }
      .ledger-label { font-family: 'Inter', 'Manrope', sans-serif; }
      .ledger-panel { background: rgba(28, 27, 27, 0.92); }
      .ledger-subpanel { background: rgba(39, 38, 38, 0.92); }
      .ledger-gold-line {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(233,195,73,0.1), rgba(233,195,73,0.9), rgba(233,195,73,0.1));
      }
      .ledger-field {
        border: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(142,145,150,0.35);
        background: transparent;
        color: #e5e2e1;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.9rem 0;
        outline: none;
        transition: border-color .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
      }
      .ledger-field:focus {
        border-bottom-color: #e9c349;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 #e9c349;
      }
      .ledger-chip { background: rgba(53,53,52,0.9); }
      .ledger-metric { background: rgba(32,31,31,0.95); }
      .ledger-card { background: rgba(32,31,31,0.96); }
      .ledger-card-alt { background: rgba(42,42,42,0.96); }
      .ledger-bar {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: rgba(53,53,52,0.65);
        height: 9px;
      }
      .ledger-bar > span {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0 auto 0 0;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e9c349, #59de9b);
      }
      .ledger-toggle-active {
        background: #e9c349;
        color: #3c2f00;
      }
      .ledger-circle {
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(233,195,73,0.08), rgba(233,195,73,0) 72%);
      }
      @media (max-width: 1023px) {
        .ledger-mobile-nav { position: sticky; bottom: 0; z-index: 30; }
      }
    </style>

    <div class="border-b border-white/10">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[1440px] items-center justify-between px-4 py-4 sm:px-6">
        <a href="/" class="ledger-serif text-lg font-black tracking-tight text-[#e9c349] sm:text-2xl">MANYTOOL.NET</a>
        <div class="hidden items-center gap-8 text-sm font-semibold text-white/60 md:flex">
          <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-white">홈으로</a>
          <a href="/tools" class="transition hover:text-white">프리미엄 서비스</a>
          <a href="/what-is-manytool" class="transition hover:text-white">소개</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-[#e9c349]">
          <a href="/en/ai-manseryeok" class="rounded-full p-2 transition hover:bg-[#e9c349]/10" aria-label="English version">🌐</a>
          <a href="/" class="rounded-full p-2 transition hover:bg-[#e9c349]/10" aria-label="Back to home">⌂</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1440px] gap-0 lg:grid-cols-[240px_minmax(0,1fr)]">
      <aside class="hidden min-h-[calc(100vh-73px)] border-r border-white/8 px-5 py-8 lg:block">
        <div class="space-y-8 sticky top-[88px]">
          <div>
            <p class="ledger-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#e9c349]">운명 탐색</p>
            <div class="mt-4 h-px w-full ledger-gold-line"></div>
          </div>
          <nav class="space-y-2 text-sm text-white/55">
            <a href="#saju-form-section" class="flex items-center justify-between ledger-subpanel px-4 py-3 text-white"><span>입력 정보</span><span class="text-[#e9c349]">01</span></a>
            <a href="#saju-result-anchor" class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 transition hover:bg-white/5"><span>오늘</span><span>02</span></a>
            <a href="#fortune-grid" class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 transition hover:bg-white/5"><span>이번 주</span><span>03</span></a>
            <a href="#fortune-grid" class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 transition hover:bg-white/5"><span>이번 달</span><span>04</span></a>
            <a href="#life-stage-grid" class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 transition hover:bg-white/5"><span>중년</span><span>05</span></a>
            <a href="#life-stage-grid" class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 transition hover:bg-white/5"><span>말년</span><span>06</span></a>
          </nav>
          <div class="ledger-panel px-4 py-5 text-sm leading-6 text-white/60">
            <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#59de9b]">Report Mode</p>
            <p class="mt-3">AI 기반 성향 분석과 통계 기반 라이프 인사이트를 조합한 자기이해 리포트 형식입니다.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="#saju-form-section" class="block bg-[#e9c349] px-4 py-4 text-center text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#3c2f00] transition hover:brightness-110">정밀 분석 시작</a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div>
        <section class="px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 lg:py-12">
          <div class="grid gap-8 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.1fr)_360px]">
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div>
                <p class="ledger-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#59de9b]">기록 해석 · Korean Saju Palja · No. 2026</p>
                <h1 class="ledger-serif mt-5 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-black leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
                  AI 만세력 <span class="text-[#e9c349] italic">사주풀이</span><br />올인원 통합형
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-white/62">
                  생년월일시를 기반으로 만세력 구조를 계산하고, 오늘과 이번주, 이번달, 상반기, 하반기, 올해의 흐름을 한 장의 프리미엄 리포트로 정리합니다.
                  미래 예언이 아니라 참고용 라이프 인사이트와 데이터 기반 자기이해 도구로 설계했습니다.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="ledger-serif text-3xl italic text-[#e9c349]">01.</div>
                  <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#e9c349]">AI 기반 성향 분석</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-white/55">사주 구조와 오행 분포를 바탕으로 성향, 판단 패턴, 생활 리듬을 정리합니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="ledger-serif text-3xl italic text-[#59de9b]">02.</div>
                  <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#59de9b]">통계 기반 라이프 인사이트</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-white/55">기간별 흐름을 읽기 쉽게 나누고 재물, 관계, 일상 리듬의 변화를 점수와 해설로 보여줍니다.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-3">
                  <div class="ledger-serif text-3xl italic text-white/50">03.</div>
                  <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/70">데이터 기반 자기이해 리포트</h2>
                  <p class="text-sm leading-7 text-white/55">같은 입력에는 같은 구조가 유지되며, 시간 정보 유무에 따라 신뢰도와 입력 정확도를 분리해 표시합니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <aside class="ledger-panel px-6 py-7 text-sm leading-7 text-white/62 xl:mt-8">
              <p class="ledger-serif text-lg font-bold text-[#e9c349]">기록된 경험</p>
              <div class="mt-6 space-y-7">
                <article>
                  <div class="text-[#e9c349]">★★★★★</div>
                  <p class="mt-2 italic">“사주풀이처럼 단정적으로 말하지 않고, 구조와 흐름을 읽는 보고서처럼 보여줘서 오히려 더 신뢰감이 있었습니다.”</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#e9c349]">Analyst Review</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                  <div class="text-[#e9c349]">★★★★★</div>
                  <p class="mt-2 italic">“오늘, 이번주, 올해를 나눠서 읽게 해두니 재구매가 아니라도 다시 확인할 이유가 생겼습니다.”</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#e9c349]">Premium User</p>
                </article>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="saju-form-section" class="px-4 pb-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
          <div class="grid gap-8 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_340px]">
            <div class="ledger-panel px-5 py-6 sm:px-8 sm:py-8">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-4">
                <div>
                  <p class="ledger-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#e9c349]">1 단계 · 기록 입력</p>
                  <h2 class="ledger-serif mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">당신의 <span class="text-[#e9c349] italic">운명 좌표</span>를 입력하세요</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="min-w-[180px]">
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40"><span>입력 준비</span><span>65% 가독성</span></div>
                  <div class="mt-3 h-[2px] bg-white/10"><div class="h-full w-[65%] bg-[#e9c349]"></div></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-white/58">
                본 서비스는 참고용 자기이해 리포트입니다. AI 기반 성향 분석과 통계 기반 라이프 인사이트를 제공하며, 의학·법률·재정적 조언이나 미래 보장을 의미하지 않습니다.
              </p>

              <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
                <label class="block">
                  <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">이름 또는 닉네임</span>
                  <input id="saju-name" type="text" placeholder="예: JI-HO PARK" class="ledger-field text-lg" />
                </label>
                <div>
                  <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">달력 기준</span>
                  <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <label class="ledger-chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white"><input type="radio" name="calendar-type" value="solar" checked />양력</label>
                    <label class="ledger-chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white"><input type="radio" name="calendar-type" value="lunar" />음력</label>
                    <label id="saju-leap-wrap" class="ledger-chip hidden inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white"><input id="saju-leap-month" type="checkbox" />윤달</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]">
                <label class="block">
                  <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">생년월일</span>
                  <input id="saju-birth-date" type="date" class="ledger-field text-lg" />
                </label>
                <div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">출생 시간</span>
                    <span class="text-xs text-[#e9c349]">시주 반영</span>
                  </div>
                  <input id="saju-birth-time" type="time" class="ledger-field text-lg" />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr]">
                <div>
                  <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">전통 시각 선택</span>
                  <select id="saju-time-branch" class="ledger-field text-base">
                    <option value="">자시~해시 선택</option>
                    <option value="23:30">자시 (23:00~00:59)</option>
                    <option value="01:30">축시 (01:00~02:59)</option>
                    <option value="03:30">인시 (03:00~04:59)</option>
                    <option value="05:30">묘시 (05:00~06:59)</option>
                    <option value="07:30">진시 (07:00~08:59)</option>
                    <option value="09:30">사시 (09:00~10:59)</option>
                    <option value="11:30">오시 (11:00~12:59)</option>
                    <option value="13:30">미시 (13:00~14:59)</option>
                    <option value="15:30">신시 (15:00~16:59)</option>
                    <option value="17:30">유시 (17:00~18:59)</option>
                    <option value="19:30">술시 (19:00~20:59)</option>
                    <option value="21:30">해시 (21:00~22:59)</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <label class="block">
                  <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">출생지</span>
                  <input id="saju-birth-place" type="text" placeholder="예: 서울, 부산, 도쿄" class="ledger-field text-lg" />
                </label>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-8 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-end">
                <div>
                  <span class="ledger-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/40">성별</span>
                  <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <label class="ledger-chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white"><input type="radio" name="saju-gender" value="male" />남성</label>
                    <label class="ledger-chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white"><input type="radio" name="saju-gender" value="female" />여성</label>
                    <label class="ledger-chip inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white"><input type="radio" name="saju-gender" value="unknown" checked />선택 안 함</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/70">
                  <input id="saju-time-unknown" type="checkbox" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-white/20 bg-transparent text-[#e9c349] focus:ring-[#e9c349]" />
                  출생 시간을 모름
                </label>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_300px]">
                <div class="ledger-subpanel px-5 py-5 text-sm leading-7 text-white/60">
                  <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#59de9b]">결제 전 안내</p>
                  <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
                    <li>AI 기반 성향 분석 / 통계 기반 라이프 인사이트 / 데이터 기반 자기이해 리포트 형식으로 제공됩니다.</li>
                    <li>본 서비스는 참고용 콘텐츠이며 의학·법률·재정적 조언이 아닙니다.</li>
                    <li>결과 해석 및 활용 책임은 사용자에게 있습니다.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <button id="saju-submit" class="w-full bg-[#e9c349] px-5 py-5 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#3c2f00] transition hover:brightness-110 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:brightness-75">풀이 시작 ($29.88)</button>
                  <div id="saju-status-box" class="ledger-subpanel px-4 py-4 text-sm leading-6 text-white/70">생년월일과 시간을 입력한 뒤 버튼을 누르면 결제 또는 분석이 진행됩니다.</div>
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/40"><span id="saju-stage">입력 대기</span><span>secure archive</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <aside class="space-y-4">
              <div class="ledger-panel px-5 py-6">
                <p class="ledger-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#e9c349]">상품 구성</p>
                <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-sm text-white/64">
                  <p>오늘 / 이번주 / 이번달</p>
                  <p>상반기 / 하반기 / 올해</p>
                  <p>중년 / 말년 분석</p>
                  <p>재물운 / 관계운 / 적성 / 생활 리듬</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-8 text-6xl ledger-serif italic text-[#e9c349]">2026</div>
              </div>
              <div class="ledger-panel px-5 py-6 text-sm leading-7 text-white/60">
                <p class="ledger-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#59de9b]">정책 가드</p>
                <p class="mt-4">정확도나 미래 예측을 과장하지 않고 참고용 정보, 엔터테인먼트, 자기이해 도구로 명확히 안내합니다.</p>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section id="saju-result-anchor" class="px-4 pb-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
          <div id="saju-empty" class="ledger-panel px-6 py-16 text-center text-sm leading-7 text-white/45">아직 분석 결과가 없습니다. 결제를 마친 뒤 이 페이지로 돌아오면 자동으로 결과가 이어집니다.</div>

          <div id="saju-result" class="hidden space-y-8">
            <section class="grid gap-6 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.08fr)_360px]">
              <article class="ledger-panel px-6 py-7 sm:px-8">
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <p class="ledger-label text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#59de9b]">핵심 해석</p>
                    <h2 id="saju-headline" class="ledger-serif mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl"></h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="space-y-3 text-right">
                    <div id="saju-name-badge" class="hidden bg-white/5 px-3 py-2 text-xs font-semibold text-[#e9c349]"></div>
                    <div id="saju-badges" class="flex flex-wrap justify-end gap-2"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p id="saju-summary" class="mt-5 max-w-4xl text-base leading-8 text-white/68"></p>
                <p id="saju-personality" class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-sm leading-8 text-white/56"></p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3 border-t border-white/8 pt-6">
                  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <button id="analysis-mode-btn" type="button" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/78 transition hover:border-[#e9c349]/50">분석 모드</button>
